Interface RegDeviceContainer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Area
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AreaImpl, RegDeviceContainerImpl

    public interface RegDeviceContainer
extends NameTag
    A representation of the model object 'Name Tag Regulation'. Name tagged element contains a list of regulation devices of type IRegulationDevice

    The following features are supported:

    • Reg Device List
